replies.body:
{{champion:27}} {{summoner:6}} {{summoner:14}} 

Hard core Singed main here with 1500+ games on Singed and reached Plat 2 &amp; 3 on two other accounts last season. 


And let me tell you how easy it is for me to destroy him in top. {{champion:82}}  poses little or no real threats to Singed un-like ALOT of other top laners such as {{champion:126}} {{champion:122}} {{champion:39}} {{champion:223}} {{champion:83}} {{champion:17}} {{champion:133}} {{champion:67}} {{champion:58}} {{champion:41}} {{champion:150}} 

{{champion:82}} can't even ulti me without me just flipping him when close and running around spamming mastery's in the void while he gets high on my gas. 
His abilities are easily dodged as-well and has no real escape, stuns or gap closers that can stop me gassing him to death. 
The early turret plating and first tower blood gold add a nice extra gold income when you make him sit under turret wishing he banned him, giving you even more of an advantage while you proxy waves and let the minions crash into the tower.

I personly rate him as 3/10 threat and the lane is completely winnable without breaking a sweat. His entire kit just doesn't work well vs a Singed.


Thank you Riot for this glorious gift to Singed mains.
{{item:2319}}
